<h3>Generator Options</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code>--stimulus</code>: Generates a new Stimulus controller named accordion_controller.js and registers it for enhanced interactivity</li>
  <li><code>--directory</code>: Customize the component location (defaults to <code>app/views/rui/components</code>)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Component Properties</h3>

<h4>Accordion Container</h4>
<ul>
  <li><code>variant</code>: Visual style variants:
    <ul>
      <li><code>:contained</code>: Default style with rounded borders and shadow</li>
      <li><code>:flush</code>: Clean style without borders or shadow</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><code>classes</code>: Additional CSS classes for accordion container</li>
  <li><code>content</code>: Block content containing accordion items</li>
</ul>

<h4>Accordion Item</h4>
<ul>
  <li><code>label</code>: Title text for the accordion item</li>
  <li><code>open</code>: Boolean to set initial open state (default: false)</li>
  <li><code>content</code>: Block content for the accordion item body</li>
</ul>

